'''Bravo Three''' was the callsign of a [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] in [[Bravo Squadron/Legends|Bravo Flight]] during the last decades of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

In [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]], [[Arven Wendik/Legends|Arven Wendik]] served as Bravo Three on the [[Bravo 3/Legends|oldest]] [[N-1 starfighter/Legends|N-1 starfighter]] in the Naboo [[Naboo Royal Space Fighter Corps/Legends|corps]] around the time of the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]], and survived that conflict.
